quote><blockquote>600蚊我去租酒店唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地d房有主題喎</blockquote><br />\n樂園呀<br />\n扑野係要情調唔係主題"},{"pid":"74a7437fdc6f7957ab334c297b1d19258a272f93","tid":204211,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/004657_d73ed8d2c06baa23fd6608e0d7d22de7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F004657_d73ed8d2c06baa23fd6608e0d7d22de7.jpg&h=a35acd62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"821a79e52b7102e27db2fb8295e3f82e147f4b94","tid":204211,"uid":63618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"巴打有無用咩all book即日酒店？唔想去到先知啲資料"},{"pid":"fc576a050418eed250a8ae5951a3515abe3c707e","tid":204211,"uid":63618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有無用咩<span style=\"color: red;\">app</span> book即日酒店？唔想去到先知啲資料</blockquote>"},{"pid":"67ad025b780e4e94b2344d5fb9a308ab8f616fd2","tid":204211,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>600蚊我去租酒店唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地d房有主題喎</blockquote><br />\n樂園呀<br />\n扑野係要情調唔係主題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋求刺激呀嘛"},{"pid":"cbf304d4c789c115ef32879f10cb303c60700241","tid":204211,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"沒有錢，哪有女？"},{"pid":"ae52bbf86b96a270082e7813dcdb88f9db779429","tid":204211,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"on99酒店都係500蚊晚"}]}